data.name: INFUSION SETS
data.description:
## COMPOSITION
- PVC, PVC DEHP-FREE (Non-Phthalate) and PVC-FREE

## STERILIZATION
- Ethylene Oxide (EO) Sterile

## PRESENTATIONS
- Fully Customizable Configurations
- Gravity and Pump
- TRANSPARENT and UV-LIGHT PROOF Tubing Finish
- Soft and Hard Tubing

## PERFORMANCE
- High Tube Memory kink-resistant
- Clear Tube and Chamber
- Clean shaped smooth surfaced components
